31
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:09,000
My brother just got a new sailboat.

32
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:12,000
He has no idea what he just got himself into.

33
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:15,000
There's nothing harder than taking care of a boat.

34
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:17,000
Am I right?

35
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:19,000
Unbelievable!

36
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:21,000
Un-be-lie-va-ble!

37
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:29,000
It is the end of the day.

38
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:31,000
It is the end of the week.

39
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:34,000
We managed to fill 40 hours, somehow.

40
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:36,000
That's not bad, is it?

41
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,000
That's great.

42
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:40,000
Pretty good.

43
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,000
Well, thank you.

44
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,000
This is very helpful feedback.

45
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:46,000
