47
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,000
Gosh, you jumped to conclusions.

48
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,000
Come on, I know.

49
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:54,000
You've got so much on your plate.

50
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:56,000
It's right now you're like,

51
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,000
What's more important, Dwight's question?

52
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,000
Figure out who's the VP.

53
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:04,000
Dwight VP, Dwight VP, Dwight VP, Dwight VP.

54
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,000
I can't be hypnotized, Dwight.

55
