Maybe go out for a little dance.

95
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,000
Beautiful day, now.

96
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:29,000
Okay, everybody, five o'clock, workday's over.

97
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:33,000
Put your pencils down and bring them back up,

98
