149
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,000
No, they're not transferable just because I handed them to you.

150
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,000
Well, that's how I played it in college.

151
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,000
College rules.

152
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:38,000
And he lost at his own lame game.

153
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:41,000
Oh, double meaning.

154
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:44,000
The game was lame and now he's lame from the kick.

155
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,000
Quick, a wick.

156
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,000
Thank you.

157
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:50,000
I will have a glass of your okiest chardonnay, please.

158
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:53,000
