159
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,000
Sorry, no waffles.

160
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:58,000
Oh, okay, just forget it then.

161
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,000
Forget it. Forget it.

162
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,000
A waffle?

163
