if she didn't want me to make some sort of last ditch,

175
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,000
nothing to lose, Kelly kahoo run at her?

176
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,000
Hey.

177
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,000
Hey.

178
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,000
Watson, carpet and tile.

179
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,000
One order.

180
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:37,000
Order of reference number 00983-126.

181
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:39,000
Eight cases, bright white inkjet.

182
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,000
Paid.

183
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,000
I'm dying!

184
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,000
Processed.

185
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,000
And delivered.

186
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:48,000
Sometimes I get so bored, I just want to scream.

187
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,000
And then sometimes I actually do scream.

188
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:53,000
I just sort of feel out what the situation calls for.

189
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,000
I will be right back.

190
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,000
I will be here.

191
